## Dataset Attribution

This project uses publicly available datasets:

- **SWAT Dataset:** Mathur & Tippenhauer, "Evasion Attacks Against Machine Learning at Test Time", 2025
  - Available: https://itrust.sutd.edu.sg/datasets/
  - License: Research Use Only

- **AI Dataset (Synchrophasor + Solar):** NREL
  - Available: https://www.nrel.gov/
  - License: CC0 Public Domain

- **NASA IMS Bearings Dataset:** NASA Prognostics Data Repository
  - Available: https://www.nasa.gov/
  - License: Public Domain

